      • readVotes

        public boolean readVotes()
                  throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        Reads the appropriate votes from the ballot and creates a new Vote by calling addVote method. sets the name of the pollingPlace to the according to the value entered by the user during creation. Also handles any small mistakes in the spelling during vote cast according to the spec that there could be utmost 3 edit distances. Also converts any empty spaces, to "-".
        Returns:
        true when successfully read.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException

      • processVotes

        public void processVotes()
        Process the votes by checking the first to n preferences. Adds all the processed n preference elements in the ArrayList referred to as priorityVotes that contains a list of Maps of {Candidate->Votes} pairs.

      • addVote
